{"lemma":"فَصِيلٌ","slug":"فَصِيلٌ","root":"ف.ص.ل","root_slug":"ف-ص-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ص-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n34004"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%B5%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%84%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"weaned young camel","examples":[{"text":"مَنْ تَصَدَّقَ بِصَدَقَةٍ مِنْ كَسْبٍ طَيِّبٍ - وَلَا يَقْبَلُ اللَّهُ إِلَّا طَيِّبًا - كَانَ إِنَّمَا يَضَعُهَا فِي كَفِّ الرَّحْمَنِ يُرَبِّيهَا كَمَا يُرَبِّي أَحَدُكُمْ فَلُوَّهُ أَوْ فَصِيلَهُ حَتَّى تَكُونَ مِثْلَ الْجَبَلِ.","english":"Whoever gives handout from good earning – and Allah only accepts the good – it is as if he placed it in the palm of the Merciful to raise it, as one of you raises his foal or young camel until it is like the mountain."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/fa.sˤiːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n34004","headword_ar":"فصِيلٌ","root":"fSl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A young camel when weaned from his mother:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Mgh, * O, K, TA:) and some times"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such a young one of the bovine kind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [and by a proleptic application,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a young camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in a general sense], because he is, or will be, weaned from his mother: (Msb:) [in the T, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuwaArN","text_ar":"حُوَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"page_break","n":2407},{"kind":"text","text":"and in other lexicons &c., it is applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a young, newly-born, camel:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in the L, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suxodN","text_ar":"سُخْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", to a fœtus in a she-camel's belly: see an ex. of its meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a young sucking camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"(one of many such exs.) in the first paragraph of art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rjl","text_ar":"رجل"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and a strange similar usage of the first of the following pls. in a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xasofN","text_ar":"خَسْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuSolaAnN","text_ar":"فُصْلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Sb, S, M, Mgh, O, Msb, K,) agreeably with rule, (Sb, M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiSolaAnN","text_ar":"فِصْلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Sb, Fr, M, Msb, K,) formed by likening the sing. to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guraAbN","text_ar":"غُرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"girobaAnN","text_ar":"غِرْبَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a pl., (Sb, M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiSaAlN","text_ar":"فِصَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Sb, S, M, Msb, K,) as though it were an epithet, (Sb, M, Msb,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kariymN","text_ar":"كَرِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kiraAmN","text_ar":"كِرَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is a pl.: (Msb:) and the female is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSiylapN","text_ar":"فَصِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAy^iT","text_ar":"حَايِط"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wall of enclosure"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (M, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having little height,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in front of, a fortress;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) or (K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in front of, the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"main"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wall of a city"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"town."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wav~aquwA suwra Almadiynapi bikibaA$K","text_ar":"وَثَّقُوا سُورَ المَدِينَةِ بِكِبَاشٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wafaSiylK","text_ar":"وَفَصِيلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They strengthened the wall of the city by means of buttresses and a low wall in front of it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece"},{"kind":"text","text":"of stone; of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylN","text_ar":"فَعِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEuwlN","text_ar":"مَفْعُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","Msb","Sb","S","M","Mgh","O","K","Fr"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}